title: Ichiban Sichuan Chinese Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Japanese, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Japanese/Szechuan restaurant offers several vegan sushi roll choices, as well as Szechuan dishes (some under the "vegetables" heading on the menu, but also some rice and noodle dishes allow a choice of protein including tofu).
